title: Country musician Todd Snider visits Birmingham's Forum Theatre in final tour
text:
Published By: Al.com: Alabama Entertainment - Today 
The newly renovated theatre welcomed East Nashville singer-songwriter Todd Snider as its first headliner Sunday night....
